Recommendations for New Recovery High Schools in
Fiscal Year 2023 and Fiscal Year 2024
The Department is currently in discussions with school districts, RHS programs, and other
partners to determine how, collectively, to best meet the needs of students with a
substance use disorder. At this time, a new RHS program is not recommended as the
Department continues to evaluate these programs and establish best practices.
